Package course

Provides classes for the course.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Course
    Holds all the methods associated with a course.
    CourseAccessor
    Provides fetch access to course data.
    CourseModifier
    Changes course data.
    CourseSnapshot
    A read only version of the course for students.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractCourse
    A Course consists of several fields necessary for class organization.
    AbstractCourseSnapshot
    A read only version of the course for students.
    CurveSetting
    Grading curve setting for a Course.
    GradeSchema
    A GradeSchema contains a function to convert a raw score to a LetterGrade.
    LatePolicy
    A policy for calculating a grade penalty on late assignments.
    LetterGrade
    A LetterGrade implements GraderData to provide a letter grade to gradable items.
